---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "PRF Microneedling | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "PRF Microneedling combines microneedling with platelet‑rich fibrin to rejuvenate skin and support natural healing.", "canonical": "/services/prf-microneedling", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate paper">

<style is:global>
  :root{ --paper:#F8F6F2; --ink:#141414; --muted:#5a5a5a; --rule:#E6E1D8; }
  .paper{ background:var(--paper); color:var(--ink); }
  .rule{ border-color:var(--rule); }
  .muted{ color:var(--muted); }
  .measure{ max-width: 64ch; }
  .dropcap:first-letter{ float:left; font-size:3.2rem; line-height:1; padding-right:.35rem; padding-top:.2rem; font-weight:600; }
  .ataglance{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.75rem 1.25rem; font-size:.95rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span::after{ content:"·"; margin-left:1.25rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span:last-child::after{ content:""; margin:0; }
  .pullquote{ border-left:2px solid var(--ink); padding-left:.85rem; font-style:italic; color:#3b3b3b; margin: 1.25rem 0; }
  .icon-check{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; flex:0 0 auto; margin-top:.15rem;}
  .timeline{ position:relative; }
  .timeline::before{ content:""; position:absolute; left:.9rem; top:.25rem; bottom:.25rem; width:2px; background:var(--rule); }
  .tl-step{ position:relative; padding-left:2.25rem; }
  .tl-badge{ position:absolute; left:0; top:.1rem; width:1.8rem; height:1.8rem; border-radius:999px; background:var(--ink); color:#fff; font-size:.9rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-weight:600; }
  .tl-title{ font-weight:600; }
  details.faq summary{ list-style:none; }
  details.faq summary::-webkit-details-marker{ display:none; }
</style>

  <div class="px-6 pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="service-head">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
    <div class="service-hero">
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-cyan-400"></span>
        <div class="service-hero v4 border-l-4 border-neutral-200 dark:border-white/10 pl-5 md:pl-6">
  <div class="service-hero v5">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
    <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.20em] text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-200">Service</span>
    <h1 class="mt-5 text-5xl md:text-7xl font-semibold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight">PRF Microneedling</h1>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-4 h-1 w-16 rounded-full bg-neutral-300 dark:bg-white/20"></div>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg md:text-xl muted leading-relaxed">Platelet‑Rich Fibrin (PRF) Microneedling is a next‑generation treatment combining collagen induction therapy with your body’s fibrin‑rich platelets and stem cells to enhance skin rejuvenation and natural healing.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 border-t rule"></div>
</div>

  <div class="mt-6 h-px bg-neutral-200/80 dark:bg-white/10"></div>
</div>

    </div>
    <div class="md:w-80">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border rule/70 bg-white/40 dark:bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 md:p-5">
        <div class="h-24 w-full rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-300/40 via-cyan-300/35 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-neutral-300/70 dark:via-white/15 to-transparent"></div>
</div>

<div class="mt-6 border-t rule"></div>
  <div class="mt-6 border-t rule"></div>
</div>

      <div class="mt-6 h-px w-full border-t rule"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-24 grid grid-cols-12 gap-8">
    <article class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 xl:col-span-7">
      <section id="description" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Description</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 muted dropcap">
          PRF Microneedling uses Platelet‑Rich Fibrin, a concentration of platelets, white blood cells, and stem cells derived from your own blood. Unlike PRP, PRF contains no additives or anticoagulants and forms a fibrin matrix that gradually releases growth factors over 7–10 days. Combined with microneedling, this allows regenerative cells to penetrate micro‑channels in the skin and stimulate collagen and elastin production.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 muted">
          The result is natural improvement in fine lines, scars, and overall tone. PRF can also be applied to the scalp to support hair restoration by nourishing follicles and promoting growth. Its autologous nature makes it safe, biocompatible, and highly effective for skin renewal.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <section id="benefits" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Benefits</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-10 gap-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>All‑natural with no synthetic additives.</div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Releases growth factors slowly for longer rejuvenation.</div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Improves wrinkles, scars, tone, and texture.</div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Safe and biocompatible.</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <section id="process" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">The Process</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 timeline space-y-6">
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">1</div><p class="tl-title">Blood Draw & Preparation</p><p class="muted mt-1">A small blood sample is collected and spun at low speed to isolate PRF with its fibrin and regenerative cells.</p></div>
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">2</div><p class="tl-title">Microneedling & PRF Application</p><p class="muted mt-1">Tiny controlled micro‑channels are created in the skin. PRF is applied and absorbed deeply into these channels, stimulating repair.</p></div>
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">3</div><p class="tl-title">Healing & Renewal</p><p class="muted mt-1">PRF slowly releases growth factors over a week, amplifying collagen production and skin rejuvenation.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <section id="care" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Pre and Post‑Treatment Instructions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
          <div><p class="font-medium">Before your visit</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 muted mt-2 space-y-2">
              <li>Avoid retinoids and harsh actives for 5–7 days.</li>
              <li>Refrain from blood‑thinning meds or supplements if safe to do so.</li>
              <li>Stay hydrated and arrive with clean, product‑free skin.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div><p class="font-medium">After your visit</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 muted mt-2 space-y-2">
              <li>Expect redness or sensitivity for 1–2 days.</li>
              <li>Avoid sun exposure, makeup, and strenuous exercise for 24–48 hours.</li>
              <li>Use gentle, hydrating skincare and daily SPF.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <section id="faqs" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">How is PRF different from PRP?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">PRF is spun slower, without additives, and provides higher growth factors released over days versus PRP’s quick release. It is considered a next‑generation treatment.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">Is PRF Microneedling safe?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Yes, it uses your own blood components and is biocompatible, reducing allergy or rejection risk.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">What areas can be treated?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Commonly face, under‑eyes, neck, and scalp for hair support.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">How many sessions do I need?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Typically 3–4 sessions spaced weeks apart, then maintenance as needed.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">Downtime?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Mild redness and sensitivity for 1–2 days; makeup may be resumed after ~24 hours.</p></details>
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
